        <abstract> 
<p>Apologises for not having answered CD’s letters of 19 December [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">13564</hi>] and 4 January [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">13599</hi>] sooner.</p>  
<p>Gives the results of his crossing experiments with <hi rend="italic">Pontederia (Eichhornia) crassipes</hi> and <hi rend="italic">P. azurea</hi>. Has also begun experiments on <hi rend="italic">Heteranthera reniformis</hi>.</p>  
<p>Thanks CD for sending three parts of the first volume of Bentham and Hooker’s <hi rend="italic">Genera plantarum</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
